OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWithin days we were in     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhell, says French mayor    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Zartoshte Bakhtiari says he hasn't     
OL,6, slept more than three hours a night    
OL,7, since the riots in France began a week 
OL,8, ago.                                   
OL,10,FBy day, he's the mayor of              
OL,11,FNeuilly-sur-Marne, in one of France's  
OL,12,Fpoorest areas, east of Paris.          
OL,14,FBy night, he patrols the streets with a
OL,15,Fdozen staff and city councillors until 
OL,16,F04:00 or 05:00, acting as an early     
OL,17,Fwarning system for police taking on the
OL,18,Frioters there.                         
OL,20,F"Within days, we (were) in hell," he   
OL,21,Ftells me.                              
